1. *Tražiti* je najteži deo. (Searching is the hardest part.)
2. On je *tražio* da se ispričamo. (He asked that we apologize.)
3. *Tražili* smo odgovor od njega. (We asked for an answer from him.)
4. Nismo *tražili* da bude tako. (We didn't ask for it to be like that.)
5. *Traženog* odgovora nismo dobili. (We didn't get the requested answer.)